{"tid":1695150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪仲要堅持black bloc","createTime":"2019-11-05T13:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:22:19.000Z","uid":248275,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ef92da7e52033e4986cfa4b10f9a399df3da3b72","tid":1695150,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"好處：sense of unity<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">然後呢？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼見情況係警察濫捕，見黑衫/後生就鳩拉鳩打，反而甚少跟服飾去秋後嘅case。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時唔知大家覺唔覺好多時<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">街坊仲霸氣過black bloc手足</span></span>。<br />\n好多時街坊屌走警察，反而手足有gear就跑到腎虧。（屌你發夢戴口罩跑到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好明顯警察（甚至已經冇乜撚用嘅藍色民意）已經自動將black bloc敵化左，變左一見到就想狗衝嘅對象，<span style=\"color: gold;\">冇左每個人身分嘅背後價值</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗下當警察見到每個人身上寫住「老師」、「餐廳老闆」、「銀行職員」、「巴士司機」、「媽媽」等等，我諗會有分別。（雖然佢地已經冇撚哂人性）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家唔需要大家真係貼自己個職業或者身分出黎，但想大家反思下black bloc仲有冇意義，定有其他方法救到更多手足/更有效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打出黎歡迎任屌，我雖然都驚比人屌、比手足當三毛，但依家真係乜柒都要試下，驚就唔講點對得住受傷被捕嘅手足。"},{"pid":"1d4539c430fd0f426b647511b215eb1fdd1260af","tid":1695150,"uid":9457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n降低成功控罪機會"},{"pid":"f7cea3c4e2c6cfbf08366be918383a1082fbbec5","tid":1695150,"uid":146917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d4539c430fd0f426b647511b215eb1fdd1260af","tid":1695150,"uid":9457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n降低成功控罪機會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"11136bd4a2ad29621f73a041b5bd0282874b9d61","tid":1695150,"uid":303463,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"都話彩虹戰衣外面著黑色褸落"},{"pid":"194179f44ff8f53565362f3ae577fdcbdd6e1e31","tid":1695150,"uid":169079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"一舊水黑風嬲，完"},{"pid":"fca9cfcfab00d6e9ad86f1ce6e90feb9e2677080","tid":1695150,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:05:54.000Z","msg":"Black bloc有咩用都唔知唔好晒時間啦"},{"pid":"c38034da5d3612b91981ab6a79ff7637f5a9628c","tid":1695150,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d4539c430fd0f426b647511b215eb1fdd1260af","tid":1695150,"uid":9457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n降低成功控罪機會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"問題好多人bloc得唔3唔4"},{"pid":"75d9dbf44efa7c11034081aa227d509453c6c789","tid":1695150,"uid":61690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"black block唔係唔得，但只限示威現場多人既時候<br />\n<br />\n相反，如果去緊/離開緊，black block反而會帶來危險，所以應該去/走都換裝（無CCTV），最簡單加件非黑色外套"},{"pid":"9bb7bfe536fd54559b86e03096432cacc11f2296","tid":1695150,"uid":103842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c38034da5d3612b91981ab6a79ff7637f5a9628c","tid":1695150,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d4539c430fd0f426b647511b215eb1fdd1260af","tid":1695150,"uid":9457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n降低成功控罪機會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"問題好多人bloc得唔3唔4"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:07:14.000Z","msg":"咁你係應該呼籲人著好D 唔係叫人唔好著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77612a8da9e797940ccdcf5e7ad04e2ca350dc2","tid":1695150,"uid":78574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"唔black bloc晨完拉鳩哂同告入哂<br />\n而家鳩拉未必告得入<br />\n不過轉下玩法都係必要嘅事"},{"pid":"ba7e4b137bf2647f14ba3d53b38edb3e2746dbf5","tid":1695150,"uid":2153,"like